simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Implements the Noop command that demonstrates the MPU9250 task is alive

simplesect.title: Command Verification
simplesect.para:
Successful execution of this command may be verified with the following telemetry:
$sc_$cpu_MPU9250_CMDACTPCNT - command counter will increment
The #MPU9250_CMD_INF_EID informational event message will be generated when the command is received

simplesect.title: Error Conditions
simplesect.para:
This command may fail for the following reason(s):
Command packet length not as expected
